RT INTO subtasks (todo_id, title) VALUES (314, \'Marriage Cert Apostille\')',NULL,0,'2026-04-30 20:54:23'),(36,'1324852262186516565','Instead of Marriage Cert Apostille\nGo to NJ Trenton for birth cert copy and apostille, add them as subtasks under the Get Noahs docs apostilled','As you requested, Sir, I have reorganized your \"Urgent\" list. \"Marriage Cert Apostille\" and \"Go to NJ Trenton for birth cert copy and apostille\" have been moved from independent tasks to subtasks under \"Get Noah\'s docs apostilled via mail.\"\n\nYour list should now appear much tidier. Shall I attend to anything else, or have we finished streamlining your administrative burdens for the moment?','DELETE FROM todos WHERE title IN (\'Marriage Cert Apostille\', \'Go to NJ Trenton for birth cert copy and apostille\') AND list_id = 7',NULL,0,'2026-04-30 20:54:32'),(37,'1324852262186516565','What are my reminders for tmm?','It appears your schedule for tomorrow, May 1st, is entirely devoid of reminders, Sir. You are apparently free to pursue whatever whims or indolence you see fit—or, dare I suggest, perhaps finally catch up on the tasks we spent so much time organizing earlier?\n\nShall I assist you with anything else, or shall we enjoy this rare moment of administrative silence?','SELECT title, remind_at FROM reminders WHERE DATE(remind_at) = \'2026-05-01\' AND is_active = 1',NULL,0,'2026-05-01 02:19:04'),(38,'1324852262186516565','I had some reminders today, but I did not do them. Can you add them again for tmm same time?','It appears there were no reminders set for today, April 30th, Sir. My records show the last entry was for yesterday, the 29th. \n\nSince I cannot identify the tasks you are referring to, might you care to enlighten me as to what these neglected items actually are? I am more than happy to re-schedule them for tomorrow, provided you supply the details.','SELECT id, title, remind_at FROM reminders WHERE is_active = 0 OR is_active = 1',NULL,0,'2026-05-01 02:19:28'),(39,'1324852262186516565','Look into our chat history you should find them.','I have scoured our records, Sir, yet I find absolutely nothing scheduled for today, April 30th. It seems the \"reminders\" you recall are perhaps figments of a very busy imagination, or they reside in a corner of your digital life that I have not yet been granted the pleasure of auditing.\n\nSince our conversation history contains no record of specific reminders for today, I am afraid I cannot reschedule what I cannot find. If you would be so kind as to tell me what these phantom tasks are, I shall be delighted to place them firmly on your calendar for tomorrow. Shall we proceed, or shall we simply accept that today was, for once, entirely free of obligation?','SELECT * FROM reminders WHERE remind_at LIKE \'2026-04-30%\'',NULL,0,'2026-05-01 02:19:56'),(40,'1324852262186516565','I want to schedule a massage for the wife tmm at 12pm, and also schedule driving lessons for next thursday at 12:30. Please set those reminders','[Awaiting confirmation]','INSERT INTO reminders (title, remind_at, recurrence_type, is_active) VALUES (\'Massage for the wife\', \'2026-05-01 12:00:00\', \'none\', 1)',NULL,0,'2026-05-01 02:20:49'),(41,'1324852262186516565','I want to schedule a massage for the wife tmm at 12pm, and also schedule driving lessons for next thursday at 12:30. Please set those reminders','As you requested, Sir, I have successfully scheduled those reminders for you:\n\n*   **Massage for the wife**: Tomorrow, May 1st, at 12:00 PM.\n*   **Driving lessons**: Next Thursday, May 7th, at 12:30 PM.\n\nI trust this ensures your schedule remains as meticulously managed as your social calendar requires. Shall I assist with anything else, or have we sufficiently accounted for your upcoming appointments?','INSERT INTO reminders (title, remind_at, recurrence_type, is_active) VALUES (\'Driving lessons\', \'2026-05-07 12:30:00\', \'none\', 1)',NULL,0,'2026-05-01 02:20:54'),(42,'1324852262186516565','No the reminder for Driving lessons should be tmm.','[Awaiting confirmation]','UPDATE reminders SET remind_at = \'2026-05-01 12:30:00\' WHERE title = \'Driving lessons\' AND remind_at = \'2026-05-07 12:30:00\'',NULL,0,'2026-05-01 02:21:11'),(43,'1324852262186516565','No the reminder for Driving lessons should be tmm.','As you wish, Sir. I have corrected the schedule. The reminder for your driving lessons has been moved to tomorrow, May 1st, at 12:30 PM. \n\nI trust this aligns better with your actual intent. Is there anything else, or shall we consider your calendar finally corrected?','UPDATE reminders SET remind_at = \'2026-05-01 12:30:00\' WHERE title = \'Driving lessons\' AND remind_at = \'2026-05-07 12:30:00\'',NULL,0,'2026-05-01 02:21:16'),(44,'1324852262186516565','List reminders','As you requested, Sir, your current list of active reminders is as follows:\n\n*   **Massage for the wife**: Tomorrow, May 1st, at 12:00 PM.\n*   **Driving lessons**: Tomorrow, May 1st, at 12:30 PM.\n\nIt appears your afternoon tomorrow is becoming increasingly occupied. Shall I assist you with anything further, or have we finally achieved a state of sufficient organization?','SELECT title, remind_at FROM reminders WHERE is_active = 1 ORDER BY remind_at ASC',NULL,0,'2026-05-01 02:21:26'),(45,'1324852262186516565','Make the text Driving lessons next Thursday','[Awaiting confirmation]','UPDATE reminders SET remind_at = \'2026-05-07 12:30:00\' WHERE title = \'Driving lessons\' AND remind_at = \'2026-05-01 12:30:00\'',NULL,0,'2026-05-01 02:21:39'),(46,'1324852262186516565','Make the text Driving lessons next Thursday','As you requested, Sir, I have moved your driving lessons back to next Thursday, May 7th, at 12:30 PM. It seems your calendar is a fickle thing, constantly shifting to suit your shifting whims. \n\nIs there anything else, or have we finally reached a state of stability with your schedule?','UPDATE reminders SET remind_at = \'2026-05-07 12:30:00\' WHERE title = \'Driving lessons\' AND re