22:32'),(51,'1324852262186516565','Whats the most recent entry in my journal about?','The most recent entry in your journal, Sir, is titled: **\"AI is starting to get really fun... And my son is awesome\"**.\n\nIt captures your reflections on the efficiency of \"vibe coding,\" your distractions with developing an automated newsletter and your humble servant here (instead of studying the *Book of Proof*), and a touching segment regarding young Master Noah’s development and your affection for him. \n\nA productive—if occasionally misdirected—use of time, it seems. Shall I leave you to your reflections, or is there something else you require?','SELECT title, content FROM journal_entries ORDER BY created_at DESC LIMIT 1',NULL,0,'2026-05-01 03:35:49'),(52,'1324852262186516565','list all todo categories','As you requested, Sir, here are your current to-do categories:\n\n*   **TEMP**\n*   **Urgent**\n*   **Chores**\n*   **Misc**\n*   **School/Coding**\n*   **HomeLab Additions**\n*   **Ideas**\n*   **Exersites**\n*   **Tim, Jim and Drue - And the Marvellous T-82**\n*   **Systems Programming Roadmap Tasks**\n\nAn extensive list, to be sure. One can only hope the actual execution matches the ambition of the organization. Is there a particular category you wish to address, or shall we let them sit for a bit longer?','SELECT title FROM todo_lists ORDER BY sort_order ASC',NULL,0,'2026-05-01 03:42:38'),(53,'1324852262186516565','Add to HomeLab Additions: persist reminders','[Awaiting confirmation]','INSERT INTO todos (list_id, title) VALUES ((SELECT id FROM todo_lists WHERE title = \'HomeLab Additions\'), \'persist reminders\')',NULL,0,'2026-05-01 03:43:19'),(54,'1324852262186516565','Add to HomeLab Additions: persist reminders','As you requested, Sir, I have added \"persist reminders\" to your **HomeLab Additions** list. I trust this task will receive the attention it deserves, rather than merely gathering digital dust alongside the rest. \n\nIs there anything else, or shall we 