r I think its just the created at that needs to change','[Awaiting confirmation]','UPDATE focuses SET created_at = \'2026-05-01 00:13:30\' WHERE text = \'study.com, cs:app, neural nets\'',NULL,0,'2026-05-01 04:13:31'),(64,'1324852262186516565','Try again…. There is no sort order I think its just the created at that needs to change','It appears my reliance on `sort_order` was optimistic, Sir. I have taken the liberty of updating the `created_at` timestamp for your consolidated focus entry to the present moment, which should effectively move it to the zenith of your list.\n\nI trust this resolution satisfies your requirements, or shall we continue rearranging digital furniture while the actual work waits patiently in the corner?','UPDATE focuses SET created_at = \'2026-05-01 00:13:30\' WHERE text = \'study.com, cs:app, neural nets\'',NULL,0,'2026-05-01 04:13:35'),(65,'1324852262186516565','Remind me to read cs:app tmm at 7:45am','[Awaiting confirmation]','INSERT INTO reminders (title, remind_at, recurrence_type) VALUES (\'Read CS:APP\', \'2026-05-02 07:45:00\', \'none\')',NULL,0,'2026-05-01 04:17:24'),(66,'1324852262186516565','Remind me to read cs:app tmm at 7:45am','As you requested, Sir, I have set a reminder for you to attend to your CS:APP reading tomorrow, May 2nd, at 7:45 AM. \n\nI trust this will be sufficient to prompt you into action when the time comes. Shall we consider this settled, or would you like to schedule further reminders for tasks that you might similarly delay?','INSERT INTO reminders (title, remind_at, recurrence_type) VALUES (\'Read CS:APP\', \'2026-05-02 07:45:00\', \'none\')',NULL,0,'2026-05-01 04:17:29'),(67,'1324852262186516565','List all reminders','As you wish, Sir. I have retrieved the list of your active reminders:\n\n*   **Massage for the wife**: 2026-05-01 at 12:00:00\n*   **Driving lessons for next Thurs**: 2026-05-01 at 12:30:00\n*   **Read CS:APP**: 2026-05-02 at 07:45:00\n\nIt appears your afternoon is becoming quite... busy. Sha