ALUES (\'Bring screens to work\', \'2026-05-01 17:00:00\', \'none\')',NULL,0,'2026-05-01 10:18:34'),(73,'1324852262186516565','Remind me to bring the screens to work today at 5pm','As you requested, Sir, I have added a reminder to bring the screens to work today, May 1st, at 5:00 PM. \n\nI’ve ensured it is on your schedule, so you might finally have a chance to focus on something other than digital housework. Shall we consider your day\'s logistics sorted, or are there any other items requiring my intervention?','INSERT INTO reminders (title, remind_at, recurrence_type) VALUES (\'Bring screens to work\', \'2026-05-01 17:00:00\', \'none\')',NULL,0,'2026-05-01 10:18:38'),(74,'1324852262186516565','Actually change that to 4:30pm','[Awaiting confirmation]','UPDATE reminders SET remind_at = \'2026-05-01 16:30:00\' WHERE title = \'Bring screens to work\' AND remind_at = \'2026-05-01 17:00:00\'',NULL,0,'2026-05-01 10:18:53'),(75,'1324852262186516565','Actually change that to 4:30pm','Consider it adjusted, Sir. Your reminder to bring the screens to work has been moved forward to 4:30 PM. \n\nI trust this provides enough time for you to manage your transition, unless, of course, there are further modifications you\'d like to make to your already impeccably curated itinerary?','UPDATE reminders SET remind_at = \'2026-05-01 16:30:00\' WHERE title = \'Bring screens to work\' AND remind_at = \'2026-05-01 17:00:00\'',NULL,0,'2026-05-01 10:18:59'),(76,'1324852262186516565','List reminders','As you wish, Sir. I have retrieved the list of your active reminders for the remainder of the day:\n\n*   **Read CS:APP**: 2026-05-01 at 07:45:00\n*   **Massage for the wife**: 2026-05-01 at 12:00:00\n*   **Driving lessons for next Thurs**: 2026-05-01 at 12:30:00\n*   **Bring screens to work**: 2026-05-01 at 16:30:00\n\nYour itinerary appears to be quite well-structured for the time being. Shall we proceed with your day, or is there another minor detail that requires my intervention?','SELECT id, title, remind_at, recurrence_type FROM reminders WHERE is_active = 1 ORDER BY remind_at ASC',NULL,0,'2026-05-01 10:19:05'),(77,'1324852262186516565','List my chores','As you wish, Sir. I have assembled your current list of responsibilities. It appears your day remains as demanding as ever:\n\n*   **Massage for the wife**: 2026-05-01 at 12:00:00\n*   **Driving lessons for next Thurs**: 2026-05-01 at 12:30:00\n*   **Bring screens to work**: 2026-05-01 at 16:30:00\n\nI trust you\'ll find a way to manage these with your usual aplomb. Shall I assist with anything else, or are you prepared to actually begin one of these tasks?','SELECT id, title, remind_at FROM reminders WHERE is_active = 1 ORDER BY remind_at ASC',NULL,0,'2026-05-01 12:38:54'),(78,'1324852262186516565','These are reminders. I meant chores from the todos','My apologies, Sir. It appears I have conflated your time-sensitive reminders with your rather expansive list of lingering chores. I have retrieved your current to-do list:\n\n*   **Persist reminders**\n*   **Complete DB Management Class - Friday (wo assignments)**\n*   **OOB (Out-of-Band) Swaps in HTMX for the MCP stack**\n*   **Get driving lessons for next Thursday**\n*   **Birkensocks?**\n*   **Calculate the total operational cost so that we can have the app pay for itself.**\n*   **Save all code on local version control to Google Drive**\n*   **C Fundamentals**\n*   **Check on taxes - federal and state taxes have not been submitted**\n*   **Tools to check out**\n*   **Networking & Sockets**\n*   **2 hour CS:APP reading for malloc project**\n*   **Get Tickets for vacation**\n*   **Mac Studio Ventures**\n*   **Write a 3 day program for Jordan Knitzer**\n*   **Get Noah\'s docs apostilled via mail**\n*   **Concurrency & Multithreading**\n*   **Memory & Systems**\n*   **Figure out how to start the process for Norwegian Passport via mail**\n*   **NEOVIM**\n*   **OS-Adjacent**\n*   **Closer to GIOS Project Territory**\n*   **Send $40 to the shitty management company**\n*   **Automated Jarvis Tickets**\n*   **Build a Neural Network in C**\n*   **Automated potential overreactions in market trends**\n*   **Check the sound bar resale price**\n*   **Look into how to do researchiq faster**\n*   **The MCP Stack Itself**\n*   **Buy Baby room things**\n*   **Buy organizers for home**\n*   **Watch the 11h vid (download it?)**\n*   **Get the photos ordered**\n*   **Get rid of desk**\n*   **Email TJ**\n*   **Skim Chapter 24 and 26 K.N King**\n*   **Call TESU and make sure you get some real numbers on transferring to TESU**\n*   **Check this out for stm32 simulation: [FreeRTOS-STM32-VSCode-Wokwi](https://github.com/KhalilOuali/FreeRTOS-STM32-VSCode-Wokwi)**\n\nIt is quite an exhaustive collection of tasks, Sir. Shall we begin tackling them, or would you prefer to spend your time organizing the list further?','SELECT title, description FROM todos WHERE is_done = 0 ORDER BY sort_order ASC',NULL,0,'2026-05-01 12:39:09'),(79,'1324852262186516565','Add a task to Chores category: write Hyrox program','[Awaiting confirmation]','INSERT INTO todos (title, list_id) VALUES (\'write Hyrox program\', 1)',NULL,0,'2026-05-02 14:51:07'),(80,'1324852262186516565','Add a task to Chores category: write Hyrox program','As you requested, Sir, I have added \"write Hyrox program\" to your Chores list. \n\nYour to-do list grows ever more expansive. Shall we get to work, or are there further additions to make before you decide to actually begin one of these tasks?','INSERT INTO todos (title, list_id) VALUES (\'write Hyrox program\', 35)',NULL,0,'2026-05-02 14:51:15'),(81,'1324852262186516565','Remind me to buy the plane tickets tmm at noon','[Awaiting confirmation]','INSERT INTO reminders (title, remind_at, recurrence_type) VALUES (\'Buy plane tickets\', \'2026-05-04 12:00:00\', \'none\')',NULL,0,'2026-05-04 02:03:30'),(82,'1324852262186516565','Remind me to buy the plane tickets tmm at noon','As requested, Sir, I have added a reminder to buy your plane tickets for tomorrow, May 4th, at 12:00 PM.\n\nI trust this will prevent any last-minute travel complications. Shall we consider your schedule finalized, or are there further logistical hurdles you would like me to clear for you?','INSERT INTO reminders (title, remind_at, recurrence_type) VALUES (\'Buy plane tickets\', \'2026-05-04 12:00:00\', \'none\')',NULL,0,'2026-05-04 02:03:32'),(83,'1324852262186516565','Remind me to text Mike Seckler tmm at noon','[Awaiting confirmation]','INSERT INTO reminders (title, remind_at, recurrence_type) VALUES (\'Text Mike Seckler\', \'2026-05-05 12:00:00\', \'none\')',NULL,0,'2026-05-05 01:58:17'),(84,'1324852262186516565','Remind me to text Mike Seckler tmm at noon','As you requested, Sir, I have added a reminder to text Mike Seckler for tomorrow, May 5th, at 12:00 PM. \n\nI trust this will be handled with your usual efficiency, provided you don\'t get distracted by the myriad of other tasks currently cluttering your agenda. Shall we consider your schedule set for the moment, or is there another minor detail that requires my intervention?','INSERT INTO reminders (title, remind_at, recurrence_type) VALUES (\'Text Mike Seckler\', \'2026-05-05 12:00:00\', \'none\')',NULL,0,'2026-05-05 01:58:21'),(85,'1324852262186516565','Add a subtask to that todo \"refer to Claude message\"','[Awaiting confirmation]','INSERT INTO subtasks (todo_id, title) VALUES (320, \'refer to Claude message\')',NULL,0,'2026-05-05 01:59:00'),(86,'1324852262186516565','Add a subtask to that todo \"refer to Claude message\"','As requested, Sir, I have added the subtask \"refer to Claude message\" to your \"write Hyrox program\" task.\n\nYour ability to delegate and structure your efforts is noted, though I suspect the actual execution remains a separate matter entirely. Is there anything else you require, or shall we let the list stand for now?','INSERT INTO subtasks (todo_id, title) VALUES (320, \'refer to Claude message\')',NULL,0,'2026-05-05 01:59:05'),(87,'1324852262186516565','Jarvis, remind me to call SAS tmm at 7am','[Awaiting confirmation]','INSERT INTO reminders (title, remind_at, recurrence_type) VALUES (\'Call SAS\', \'2026-05-10 07:00:00\', \'none\')',NULL,0,'2026-05-09 23:19:32'),(88,'1324852262186516565','Jarvis, remind me to call SAS tmm at 7am','As you requested, Sir, I have set a reminder to call SAS for tomorrow, May 10th, at 07:00 AM. \n\nI trust you\'ll be awake and functional by then, though given your current trajectory, I shan\'t hold my breath. Shall I see to anything else, or is this the extent of your administrative requirements for the evening?','INSERT INTO reminders (title, remind_at, recurrence_type) VALUES (\'Call SAS\', \'2026-05-10 07:00:00\', \'none\')',NULL,0,'2026-05-09 23:19:35');
