 Smart Bird Feeders Everyone\\u2019s Talking About (and Actually Buying) (2026)\", \"url\": \"https://www.wired.com/story/best-smart-bird-feeders/\"}, {\"title\": \"The Best Permanent Outdoor Lights (2026): Govee, Eufy, Cync\", \"url\": \"https://www.wired.com/story/should-you-get-permanent-outdoor-lights/\"}, {\"title\": \"Suspected gunman at Washington press dinner identified as 31-year-old Californian\", \"url\": \"https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/cr717nglye0o?at_medium=RSS&at_campaign=rss\"}, {\"title\": \"Oil prices rise as US-Iran peace talks stall\", \"url\": \"https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/c15d57pv925o?at_medium=RSS&at_campaign=rss\"}, {\"title\": \"Ukraine\'s drone commander has Russian oil, troops and morale in his sights\", \"url\": \"https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/c1d9wvd2e4ro?at_medium=RSS&at_campaign=rss\"}, {\"title\": \"Pirates seize another vessel off Somali coast as threat level increased\", \"url\": \"https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/cn7871n27nlo?at_medium=RSS&at_campaign=rss\"}, {\"title\": \"Kim Jong Un opens memorial for N Korean soldiers killed in Ukraine war\", \"url\": \"https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/cql7l707244o?at_medium=RSS&at_campaign=rss\"}, {\"title\": \"Iran\\u2019s top diplomat in Russia as Tehran intensifies efforts to end the war\", \"url\": \"https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2026/4/27/iran-foreign-minister-in-russia-for-putin-talks?traffic_source=rss\"}, {\"title\": \"War and neglect fuel deadly measles epidemic in Sudan\\u2019s Darfur\", \"url\": \"https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2026/4/27/war-and-neglect-fuel-deadly-measles-epidemic-in-sudans-darfur?traffic_source=rss\"}, {\"title\": \"\\u2018I have to protect them\\u2019: The man guarding Mauritania\\u2019s rare Islamic books\", \"url\": \"https://www.aljazeera.com/features/2026/4/27/the-man-guarding-mauritanias-rare-islamic-texts?traffic_source=rss\"}, {\"title\": \"ACL injury ends Xavi Simons\\u2019 World Cup 2026 dream with the Netherlands\", \"url\": \"https://www