ZaS1RjNmxlNGJSWVJabmg4MkJvcjJJdXBQRFZDM2NaNTVza1ZubUxwUi0xckZLQmJxaWZFUlB3RkZ5VnBfcktFR240?oc=5\"}, {\"title\": \"Trump says the U.S will \'guide\' stranded ships from the Strait of Hormuz - NPR\", \"url\": \"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMickFVX3lxTE5LVVAyU3M0aXd3SXhIeENwUHNzWUJGY2ltS0lmYTVrbHZsZ2tIYnUzc0NlM3RZb1BOdjBoMlBYZ1drTnRLcVptUldvMS1qc1VmUjJPVHBlXzZFcG9LOGlPcHloVVQ0Z0RGeTRMUUxQNEhMUQ?oc=5\"}, {\"title\": \"Trump: Latest Iran terms unacceptable; US on Monday to start guiding ships out of Hormuz - The Times of Israel\", \"url\": \"https://news.google.?oc=5\"}, {\"title\": \"Trump\\u2019s Disapproval Rating Hits New High In Latest Poll - Forbes\", \"url\": \"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMipwFBVV95cUxOOHc5bEFCUzRjRWhVMml1dFNmeFpPYkFybFBVWGxoR2FxNVptRXczenlJS04waUtLbzhCcF9NNGNsTWhUc0czeUxkNGVFbWJxalR2REpjUW9oZUZJbGl5MW80X3RNSXFHdEJQV1kyUmN0Y1hrWGFvOXgwNmpuOURackJpMC1iVGdrNzBzOXV5R04xRnZKTXBKTUhPdllwdkFxc2lpZnZuMA?oc=5\"}, {\"title\": \"Secret Service agent hit by buckshot from the gun of man charged in correspondents\' dinner attack, prosecutor says - PBS\", \"url\": \"https://news.google.?oc=5\"}]','2026-05-04 09:00:14'),(40,'Daily Planet - May 05, 2026','### Global Crisis and Geopolitical Instability\nThe global landscape is facing a volatile start to the week, headlined by a significant escalation in the Middle East. The U.S. Navy has reportedly sunk seven small Iranian boats following a series of Iranian-led attacks on the United Arab Emirates and international shipping lanes within the Strait of Hormuz. The international community has responded with widespread condemnation, characterizing the move as a dangerous escalation of maritime conflict.\n\nElsewhere, domestic tensions have flared in the United States, where a man was wounded after allegedly opening fire near the White House, resulting in a bystander also being struck by gunfire. In international humanitarian and security reports, Afghanistan has accused Pakistan of killing three civilians in an incident described as a \"war crime.\" Meanwhile, Gaza’s refugee camps face a growing public health crisis as summer temperatures rise, facilitating the spread of skin diseases.\n\n### Technology: Innovation, IPOs, and Industrial Shifts\nThe technology sector remains in a period of intense financial and structural movement. Geothermal energy startup Fervo Energy is signaling the sector\'s maturation with plans for an IPO valued at up to $1.3 billion. Simultaneously, Cerebras is preparing for a blockbuster public offering, bolstered by its deepening partnership with OpenAI.\n\nIn the industry at large, Nvidia CEO Jensen Huang has pushed back against the pervasive anxiety regarding AI-driven unemployment, arguing instead that artificial intelligence is acting as a catalyst for significant job creation. Data trends suggest that the focus is shifting away from chatbot iteration, with image-based AI models currently driving the most substantial growth in application usage. In infrastructure, security teams are managing a severe vulnerability—dubbed \"CopyFail\"—affecting major Linux distributions, while Valve has been observed importing 50 tons of game consoles, hinting at significant supply chain movement.\n\n### Quick Hits\n*   **Legal & Corporate:** Elon Musk is set to settle the SEC’s Twitter lawsuit for a nominal $1.5 million penalty. OpenAI’s leadership remains under scrutiny, with President Greg Brockman facing criticism for sidestepping direct inquiries during ongoing proceedings. \n*   **Civic & Cultural:** The Supreme Court has cleared the way for Louisiana to redraw its electoral map, a move that will reshape the state’s redistricting fight. Meanwhile, the 2025 Pulitzer Prizes have been awarded, recognizing excellence in reporting from outlets including the AP, *The Washington Post*, and Reuters.\n*   **Tragedy & Incident:** A devastating explosion at a Chinese fireworks factory has claimed 26 lives, and a vehicle-ramming incident in Leipzig, Germany, has resulted in multiple casualties. In Australia, a yacht sinking has left three dead, including members of the rescue team.\n*   **Consumer Picks:** With Mother\'s Day approaching, interest in smart-home utility—specifically the Skylight 15-inch smart calendar—is peaking as it hits record-low pricing. Various promotional incentives are also active across tech peripherals, including Loop Earplugs and Meta Quest hardware.','[{\"title\": \"Async Rust never left the MVP state\", \"url\": \"https://tweedegolf.nl/en/blog/237/async-rust-never-left-the-mvp-state\"}, {\"title\": \"Train Your Own LLM from Scratch\", \"url\": \"https://github.com/angelos-p/llm-from-scratch\"}, {\"title\": \"Hand Drawn QR Codes\", \"url\": \"https://sethmlarson.dev/hand-drawn-qr-codes\"}, {\"title\": \"Bun is being ported from Zig to Rust\", \"url\": \"https://github.com/oven-sh/bun/commit/46d3bc29f270fa881dd5730ef1549e88407701a5\"}, {\"title\": \"Lessons for Agentic Coding: What should we do when code is cheap?\", \"url\": \"https://www.dbreunig.com/2026/05/04/10-lessons-for-agentic-coding.html\"}, {\"title\": \"As workers worry about AI, Nvidia\\u2019s Jensen Huang says AI is \\u2018creating an enormous number of jobs\\u2019\", \"url\": \"https://techcrunch.com/2026/05/04/as-workers-worry-about-ai-nvidias-jensen-huang-says-ai-is-creating-an-enormous-number-of-jobs/\"}, {\"title\": \"Geothermal startup Fervo Energy to raise up to $1.3B in IPO\", \"url\": \"https://techcrunch.com/2026/05/04/geothermal-startup-fervo-energy-to-raise-up-to-1-3b-in-ipo/\"}, {\"title\": \"US government warns of severe CopyFail bug affecting major versions of Linux\", \"url\": \"https://techcrunch.com/2026/05/04/u-s-government-warns-of-severe-copyfail-bug-affecting-major-versions-of-linux/\"}, {\"title\": \"OpenAI\\u2019s cozy partner Cerebras is on track for a blockbuster IPO\", \"url\": \"https://techcrunch.com/2026/05/04/openais-cozy-partner-cerebras-is-on-track-for-a-blockbuster-ipo/\"}, {\"title\": \"Image AI models now drive app growth, beating chatbot upgrades\", \"url\": \"https://techcrunch.com/2026/05/04/image-ai-models-now-drive-app-growth-beating-chatbot-upgrades/\"}, {\"title\": \"The 40 best Mother\\u2019s Day gift ideas for 2026\", \"url\": \"https://www.theverge.com/gadgets/907032/best-mothers-day-gift-ideas-2026-mom-tech-gadgets\"}, {\"title\": \"Valve just imported 50 tons of game consoles in two days\", \"url\": \"https://www.theverge.com/news/923461/valve-steam-machine-frame-deck-import-records-may-2026\"}, {\"title\": \"OpenAI\\u2019s president does \\u2018all the things,\\u2019 except\\u00a0answer a question\", \"url\": \"https://www.theverge.com/ai-artificial-intelligence/923684/musk-brockman-altman-openai-trial\"}, {\"title\": \"Elon Musk will settle the feds\\u2019 Twitter lawsuit with pocket change\", \"url\": \"https://www.theverge.com/tech/923612/elon-musk-sec-1-5-million-penalty-twitter-x\"}, {\"title\": \"Skylight\\u2019s 15-inch smart calendar is down to its lowest price to date\", \"url\": \"https://www.theverge.com/gadgets/918544/skylight-15-inch-smart-calendar-2-mothers-day-deal-2026-sale\"}, {\"title\": \"Loop Earplugs Discount Codes: 40% Off\", \"url\": \"https://www.wired.com/story/loop-earplugs-discount-code/\"}, {\"title\": \"Meta Quest Promo Codes: $50 Off | May 2026\", \"url\": \"https://www.wired.com/story/meta-quest-promo-code/\"}, {\"title\": \"B&H Photo Promo Codes and Deals This May\", \"url\": \"https://www.wired.com/story/bh-photo-coupon/\"}, {\"title\": \"Exclusive Lovehoney Discount Codes: 15% Off\", \"url\": \"https://www.wired.com/story/lovehoney-discount-code/\"}, {\"title\": \"Layla Sleep Coupon: Save Up to $600 in May 2026\", \"url\": \"https://www.wired.com/story/layla-sleep-coupon/\"}, {\"title\": \"Explosion at China fireworks factory kills 26 people\", \"url\": \"https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/c70vqwengxno?at_medium=RSS&at_campaign=rss\"}, {\"title\": \"Two killed and many injured after car driven into crowd